title: 793. Breaking Down Top 10 of the Draft & Potential Pick Scenarios
itunes:title: 793. Breaking Down Top 10 of the Draft & Potential Pick Scenarios
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. Throughout the show, the guys go through the top 10 of the NFL draft after all the top free agency moves. The duo pick the potential players that the teams in the top 10 could draft. Find out who fills a need for each team in this episode.

Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
